[
    {
        "content": "<p>Should it be</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">lemma</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Int</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">two_dvd_mul_add_one</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℤ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∣</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">...</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>or</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">lemma</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Int</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">two_dvd_mul_succ_self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℤ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∣</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">...</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>? Compare the existing</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">lemma</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Int</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">even_mul_succ_self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℤ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Even</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">...</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>If we prefer the <code>add_one</code> version, should all the declarations having <code>succ</code> in the name, but <code>_ + 1</code> in the type be renamed? <span aria-label=\"innocent\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f607\" role=\"img\" title=\"innocent\">:innocent:</span></p>",
        "id": 537119004,
        "sender_full_name": "Michael Stoll",
        "timestamp": 1756736084
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think <code>add_one</code> is preferred unless you are talking about <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Nat.succ#doc\">docs#Nat.succ</a> but we aren't too strict on that</p>",
        "id": 537128254,
        "sender_full_name": "Robin Arnez",
        "timestamp": 1756738977
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Compare<br>\n<span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"644391\">@loogle</span> \"succ\", _ + 1</p>",
        "id": 537128389,
        "sender_full_name": "Robin Arnez",
        "timestamp": 1756739025
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"search\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f50d\" role=\"img\" title=\"search\">:search:</span> <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Init/Data/Nat/Basic.html#Nat.succ_eq_add_one\">Nat.succ_eq_add_one</a>, <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Init/Data/Nat/Basic.html#Nat.instNeZeroSucc\">Nat.instNeZeroSucc</a>, and <a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=%22succ%22%2C%20_%20%2B%201\">1568 more</a></p>",
        "id": 537128395,
        "sender_full_name": "loogle",
        "timestamp": 1756739027
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and<br>\n<span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"644391\">@loogle</span> \"add_one\", _ + 1</p>",
        "id": 537128474,
        "sender_full_name": "Robin Arnez",
        "timestamp": 1756739048
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"search\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f50d\" role=\"img\" title=\"search\">:search:</span> <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Init/Data/Nat/Basic.html#Nat.add_one_ne\">Nat.add_one_ne</a>, <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Init/Data/Nat/Basic.html#Nat.add_one_ne_self\">Nat.add_one_ne_self</a>, and <a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=%22add_one%22%2C%20_%20%2B%201\">512 more</a></p>",
        "id": 537128480,
        "sender_full_name": "loogle",
        "timestamp": 1756739049
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>In my opinion, we shouldn't need to talk about <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Nat.succ#doc\">docs#Nat.succ</a> outside of the most basic theory of natural numbers (which is in core). And so, we should use <code>add_one</code> everywhere, since <code>Nat.succ</code> shouldn't be appearing at all</p>",
        "id": 537128539,
        "sender_full_name": "Bhavik Mehta",
        "timestamp": 1756739077
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Should we add that to the technical debt counters? <span aria-label=\"slight smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f642\" role=\"img\" title=\"slight smile\">:slight_smile:</span></p>",
        "id": 537128666,
        "sender_full_name": "Michael Stoll",
        "timestamp": 1756739124
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"644391\">@loogle</span> Nat.succ</p>",
