    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"search\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f50d\" role=\"img\" title=\"search\">:search:</span> <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int.negSucc\">Int.negSucc</a>, <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int.negSucc.injEq\">Int.negSucc.injEq</a>, and <a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=Int.negSucc\">172 more</a></p>",
